PrecisAmendment to the AIR TRANSPORTATION TAX REGULATIONS, 1992 increasing the maximum amount of tax applicable on the transportation of a person by air to $25 from $19, in cases where the transportation is subject to the ad valorem air transportation tax imposed by the United States, and where the amount is paid or payable outside Canada.
